{{zh-hanzi|[[三]][[令]][[五]][[申]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: give three orders and five explanations

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' sān lìng wŭ shēn)
# to repeatedly [[admonish]]
# to repeatedly [[warn]]
#: ''[[尽管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[许多]][[员工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照办]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese|simplified]])
#: ''[[儘管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[許多]][[員工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照辦]].'' ([[Traditional Chinese|traditional]])
#: ''No matter how much you '''warn and admonish''' them, there are many employees who just aren't willing to do as they are told.''

